OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with late sunny then clear
OL,7,Fspells. Turning cloudier from the
OL,8,Fsouth overnight with heavy rain
OL,9,Freaching Orkney by dawn. Wind becoming
OL,10,Fstrong southeasterly with risk of
OL,11,Fgales.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FCloudy with heavy rain
OL,14,Fspreading northeast. Orkney turns dry
OL,15,Fthrough the afternoon, but rain
OL,16,Fcontinues in Shetland. Strong winds
OL,17,Ffor Orkney but gales or possibly
OL,18,Fsevere gales for Shetland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
